content.rendered:
Directed by Trivikram Srinivas.

Written by Yaddanapoodi Sulochana Rani.

Cast Nithiin(Anand Vihari). Samantha Ruth Prabhu(Anasuya Ramalingam). Anupama Parameswaran(Nagavalli (as Anupama Parameshwaran)). Nadia Moidu(Mahalakshmi). V.K. Naresh(Ramalingam (as Naresh)). Rao Ramesh(Pallam Venkanna). Srinivas Avasarala(Shekhar). Ananya(Bhanumati). Krishna Murali Posani(Pallam Narayana). Srinivasa Reddy(Gopal (as Srinivas Reddy)). Hari Teja(Mangamma). Easwari Rao(Kameshwari (as Eshwari Rao)). V. Jayaprakash(Satyawada Krishnamurthy). Ajay(Pallam Venkanna’s son) .Annapoorna.Giri Babu. Raghu Babu(Raghu). Joy Badlani(Bala Govindh (as Joy Badlani)).Chammak Chandra. Dhritiman Chatterjee(Mahadev).Gundu Hanumantha Rao.R.J. Hemant.Karate Kalyani.Hiroshini Komali.Madhunandan. Pkaushikji(Friend). Praveen(Muthyam).Rajitha.Pammi Sai.Sana.Shakalaka Shankar.Sivannarayana.Sri Sudha.Gundu Sudharshan

Languages Hindi. Telugu.

Producers S. Radha Krishna. P.D.V. Prasad.

Production Haarika & Hassine Creations.
